 Bandits allegedly killed 15 villagers, on Sunday, in attacks on Hayin Kanwa, a village in Giwa Local Government Area of Kaduna State. A source said that the bandits invaded Yakawada ward in Hayin Kanwa village stating that “The 15 people killed were buried early morning on Monday. “Killings and reported kidnapping cases in Giwa are getting out of hand as people are being killed and kidnapped daily.” However, the police were yet to react to the reported killings. 